# AvenirCore UI

- Use **CSS variables** from `:root` in `src/index.css` (e.g. `var(--color-emerald)`, `var(--color-navy)`, `var(--color-teacher)` for educator surfaces). Extend `:root` for new brand tokens instead of hardcoding hex in JSX when possible.
- Use `.container`, `.btn` / `.btn-primary`, `.section-label` where appropriate.
- Responsive: `@media (max-width: 900px)` patterns at end of relevant CSS blocks.
- Cross-page anchors: `href="/#section-id"` (leading slash).
- Full token list: `.agents/skills/avenircore-frontend-guidelines.md`.
